---
import Page from '@layouts/Page.astro';
---

<Page
  title="搜尋"
  description="搜尋國際醫療減碳協會網站的所有內容，包括新聞、知識庫、案例與服務說明。"
>
  <div class="container page-content">

    <header class="page-header">
      <h1 class="page-title">網站搜尋</h1>
      <p class="page-lead">在協會網站中搜尋您感興趣的主題。</p>
    </header>

    <div class="search-container">
      <link href="/_pagefind/pagefind-ui.css" rel="stylesheet" />
      <div id="search" class="search-widget"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="search-hints">
      <h2 class="search-hints__title">搜尋建議</h2>
      <div class="search-hints__grid">
        <a href="/glossary/" class="hint-chip">碳盤查</a>
        <a href="/glossary/" class="hint-chip">ISO 14064</a>
        <a href="/services/" class="hint-chip">ESG 報告</a>
        <a href="/services/" class="hint-chip">補助申請</a>
        <a href="/insights/" class="hint-chip">政策解讀</a>
        <a href="/case-studies/" class="hint-chip">成功案例</a>
        <a href="/news/" class="hint-chip">碳費</a>
        <a href="/insights/" class="hint-chip">淨零排放</a>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</Page>

<script>
  window.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {
    const script = document.createElement('script');
    script.src = '/_pagefind/pagefind-ui.js';
    script.onload = () => {
      // @ts-ignore
      new PagefindUI({ element: '#search', showSubResults: true });
    };
    document.head.appendChild(script);
  });
</script>

<style>
  .page-content {
    padding-block: var(--space-3xl);
  }

  .page-header {
    max-width: 72ch;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-3xl);
  }

  .page-title {
    font-size: var(--text-4xl);
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-text);
    line-height: var(--leading-tight);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .page-lead {
    font-size: var(--text-xl);
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    line-height: var(--leading-loose);
  }

  .search-container {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-3xl);
    max-width: 800px;
  }

  .search-widget {
    --pagefind-ui-primary: var(--color-primary);
    --pagefind-ui-text: var(--color-text);
    --pagefind-ui-background: var(--color-paper);
    --pagefind-ui-border: var(--color-border);
    --pagefind-ui-border-width: 1px;
    --pagefind-ui-border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    --pagefind-ui-font: var(--font-body);
  }

  .search-hints {
    padding-top: var(--space-2xl);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .search-hints__title {
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .search-hints__grid {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .hint-chip {
    padding: var(--space-sm) var(--space-lg);
    background-color: var(--color-surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: 9999px;
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--color-text);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: border-color var(--transition-fast), color var(--transition-fast), background-color var(--transition-fast);
    min-height: 36px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .hint-chip:hover {
    border-color: var(--color-primary);
    color: var(--color-primary);
    background-color: var(--color-primary-pale);
  }
</style>
